(139, 1, '2018-11-30 11:56:48', '2018-11-30 16:56:48', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":113,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":593,\"height\":457,\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/21272973_10159436107180372_8328644273903039366_o.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/21272973_10159436107180372_8328644273903039366_o.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-113\" width=\"593\" height=\"457\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Time was created for IMG -103 ;&nbsp; If for one result Bill\'s time at North Island College Has made him fall in love with Art , Feeling old Am running out of time Bill turned 50 and decided to create this piece which contains the hourglass Acquired off of the Internet , but heavily edited From its original form , A photograph of Bill Standing in front of a green screen with his hands out , The glass ball with the baby picture added later , Along with the Grim Reaper , This piece Expresses Bill\'s feeling of running out of time , but also shows Bills creative Love for art . Sadly this is all that\'s left from this project due to a hard drive crash ..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Time', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'time', '', '', '2018-12-05 20:05:16', '2018-12-06 01:05:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=139', 0, 'page', '', 0),
